data.description: Welcome to this beautiful renovated single family with detached 2 car garage and ample storage. The house offers new roof on the house and the garage, new windows beaming with sunlight on all areas and a long driveway for five cars. Come and see everything this beauty has to offers from custom two toned shaker cabinets, brand new appliances, four bedrooms, three full bathrooms, two wash/dryer connections and a full finished basement!
